'''密傳基督教'''，亦名'''密意基督教'''（{{lang-en|Esoteric Christianity}}），自[[文藝復興|文藝復興]]時期起同《[[赫密士文集|赫密士文集]]》相結合，所以又稱'''赫密士基督教'''（{{lang|en|Hermetic Christianity}}），是一種將[[基督教|基督教]]視為[[秘密宗教|祕密宗教]]的[[靈性|靈性]]流派的統稱，<ref>{{cite book |editor-last1=Faivre |editor-first1=Antoine |editor-last2=Hanegraaff |editor-first2=Wouter J. |date=1998 |title=''Western Esotericism and the Science of Religion: Selected Papers Presented at the 17th Congress of the International Association for the History of Religions, Mexico City, 1995'' |language=en |location=Leuven |publisher=Peeters Publishers |page= |isbn=9789042906303}}</ref><ref name="Besant 2001">{{cite book |last=Besant |first=Annie |title=''Esoteric Christianity or the Lesser Mysteries'' |language=en |location=Boston |publisher=Adamant Media Corporation |year=2001 |isbn=978-1-4021-0029-1}}</ref>追隨者相信並實踐特定的密傳教條和教義，<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |year=1971 |title=Esotericism |language=en |encyclopedia=''Oxford English Dictionary Compact Edition'' |volume=1 |publisher=Oxford University Press |location=Oxford |page={{p.|894}} |quote=From the Greek ἐσωτερικός (''esoterikós'', "inner"). The term ''esotericism'' itself was coined in the 17th century.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |editor-last1=Hanegraaff |editor-first1=Wouter J. |editor-last2=Faivre |editor-first2=Antoine |editor-last3=Van den Broek |editor-first3=Roelof |editor-last4=Brach |editor-first4=Jean-Pierre |date=2006-04-28 |title=''Dictionary of Gnosis & Western Esotericism'' |language=en |location=Leuven |publisher=Peeters Publishers |page= |isbn=978-90-04-15231-1}}</ref>這些教義只有少數人掌握，一般不為主流基督徒所熟知，甚至是被主流基督教所排斥的教導。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.webster.com/dictionary/esoteric |title=''Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary'': Esoteric |website=webster.com |language=en |access-date=2017-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907075009/http://www.webster.com/dictionary/esoteric |archive-date=2008-09-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

這些流派有一些共通點，比如包含非正統或被視為異端的基督教神學觀點。他們不只閱讀[[正典|正典]][[福音書|福音書]]，也會從[[偽典|偽典]]和[[次經|次經]]中尋求教導。再如「{{tsl|en|Disciplina arcani|祕傳教規}}」，一種被認為源於[[十二使徒|十二使徒]]的口述傳統，其中包含了來自[[耶穌基督|耶穌基督]]本人的密傳教導。<ref name="Stroumsa">{{cite book |last1=Stroumsa |first1=Gedaliahu A. Guy |last2=Sṭrûmzā |first2=Guy G. |date=2005 |title=''Hidden Wisdom: Esoteric Traditions and the Roots of Christian Mysticism'' |language=en |location=Leiden |publisher=Brill Publishers |page= |isbn=9789004136359}}</ref>

== 密契主義 ==
[[File:Bronnikov_gimnpifagoreizev.jpg|thumb]]對早期基督教神學家影響深遠。]]
「密契主義」，或「神祕主義」（{{lang|en|mysticism}}）一詞源自希臘文{{lang|el|μυω}}，意為「隱密」或「密藏」。<ref name="stanford">{{cite web |url=https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/mysticism/ |title=Mysticism |last=Gellman |first=Jerome |date=2004 |website=plato.stanford.edu |language=en |access-date=2020-05-21 |archive-date=2018-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911114311/https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/mysticism/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>由它派生出的{{lang|el|μυστικός}}（{{transl|el|mystikós}}）意為「經祕儀入教者」（{{lang|en|an initiate}}）。在[[希臘化時代|希臘化世界]]，{{lang|en|mystical}}指稱的就是祕密的宗教儀式，<ref name="stanford" />該詞不包含宗教或靈性的超升之意。<ref>{{cite book |last=Parsons |first=William Barclay |date=2011 |title=''Teaching Mysticism'' |language=en |location=Oxford |publisher=Oxford University Press |page={{p.|3}} |isbn=9780199751198}}</ref>一名{{transl|el|mystikós}}就是一名密契宗教的入教者。

神學家對{{lang|en|mystery}}的定義是「無法以[[理智|理智]]來解釋的超自然力量的眞理」。<ref>{{cite book |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=1911 |title=''[[天主教百科全書|The Catholic Encyclopedia]]'' |language=en |volume=5 |location=New York |publisher=Robert Appleton Company |page=}}</ref>因此，狹義上講，{{lang|en|mystery}}就是指讓受造物的智力獲得靈性超升的眞理。

== 溯源 ==
現代學者認為{{Link-en|早期正統基督教|Proto-orthodox Christianity}}自[[巴勒斯坦地區|巴勒斯坦地區]]和{{Link-en|希臘化猶太教|Hellenistic Judaism}}中繼承了一些重要的口傳教導。至公元4世紀，據信一套名為「祕傳教規」的祕密口述傳統形成。但主流派神學家認為，這種傳統只不過包含一些宗教儀式的細節，以及一些已經存在於主流基督教中的特定傳承。<ref name="Stroumsa" /><ref>{{cite book |last=Frommann |first=Ge. Carol. Lud. Th. |date=1833 |title=''De Disciplina Arcani quae in vetere Ecclesia christiana obticuisse fertur'' |language=la |location=[[耶拿|Ienae]] |publisher=Typis Schreiberi |page=}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Hatch |first=Edwin |date=1907 |chapter="Lecture X" |title=''The Influence of Greek Ideas and Usages upon the Christian Church'' |language=en |location=London |publisher=Williams and Norgate}}</ref>對密傳基督教影響深遠的早期神學家有[[亞歷山卓|亞歷山卓]]的[[克萊曼特_(亞歷山大城)|克萊芒]]和[[俄利根|俄利根]]。<ref>{{cite book |last=Daniélou |first=Jean |translator-last=Mitchell |translator-first=Walter |date=1955 |title=''Origen'' |language=en |location=London |publisher=Sheed and Ward |page= |isbn=9780404623814}}</ref>

[[諾斯底主義|諾斯底派]]的基督徒，比如{{Link-en|華倫廷派|Valentinianism}}和{{Link-en|巴西里得派|Basilideans}}，大多信仰[[轉世|輪迴轉世]]，而早期正統派基督徒則完全反對這種信仰。雖然俄利根在其著作《{{Link-en|原道論|On the First Principles}}》中表述了一種靈魂於諸世穿梭的複雜教導，但他在自己的其他著作如《{{Link-en|駁塞爾蘇|Contra Celsum}}》中明確反對轉世說。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628182538/http://www.catholic.com/library/Reincarnation.asp |title=Reincarnation |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2004 |website=catholic.com |language=en |access-date=2020-05-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.john-uebersax.com/plato/origen1.htm |title=Early Christianity and Reincarnation: Modern Misrepresentation of Quotes by Origen |last=Uebersax |first=John S. |date=2006 |website=john-uebersax.com |language=en |access-date=2020-05-21 |archive-date=2019-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826032310/http://www.john-uebersax.com/plato/origen1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

即便如此，現代諸多密傳基督教運動仍然以俄利根的著作，同時結合其他[[教父_(基督教歷史)|早期教父]]的作品和《聖經》章節，來證明類似觀點和學說存在於非諾斯底派的主流教會中。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102055758/http://www.archeosofica.org/en/index.php/Members-Area-Registred/Esoteric-Christianity.html |title=Articles on Esoteric Christianity |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=<!--Not stated--> |website=archeosofica.org |language=en |access-date=2020-05-21}}</ref>歷史學家{{Link-en|楊·璽柏思|Jan Shipps}}認為[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]就含有密契元素。<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Shipps |first=Jan |date=1978-08 |title=The Mormons: Looking Forward and Outward |language=en |magazine=''The Christian Century'' |location=Chicago |publisher=Christian Century Foundation |pages={{pp.|761|766}}}}</ref>

